Package nl.jortenmilo.command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandExecutor
    This interface is executed when a command is used.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    Command is the class that you use for creating your own commands.
    CommandAddedEvent
    This event is executed when a command is added to the CommandManager.
    CommandDecoder
    The CommandDecorder contains some methods to get the parameters from a String.
    CommandEvent
    This is the general CommandEvent.
    CommandManager
    This is the manager for all of the command related stuff.
    CommandPostExecuteEvent
    This event is executed after a command is executed.
    CommandPreExecuteEvent
    This event is executed before a command is executed.
    CommandRemovedEvent
    This event is executed when a command is removed from the CommandManager.
